Flickers mouth dropped open and he began to sob
alittle.

Flicker:  Yo-you d-don't even remember.  I wa-was
trying to protect you, but I was nearly killed by the
Ro-Rouges.  You surrendered to them to save me.  You
don't even remember?

He wants to pull her close, but doesn't want to scare
her, so he just stands there looking at her and
sobbing.
